(1, 'film_8.jpg', '<p>From film festivals to promotions and distributions, our Agency would help your project in every way.</p>', 'film_9.jpg', '<h2>The Official Agency</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>With aim&nbsp;to connect filmmakers with film festival market, you will find&nbsp;specialized&nbsp;strategies&nbsp;for each film and project and distribute them&nbsp;to renowned festivals increasing their probability of getting officially selected.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We follow transparent communication and helps filmmakers in getting branding, offers for the future projects, chance to attend screenings in international film festivals, connections &amp; leads with buyers, networking opportunities with film professionals and reviews &amp; accolades by media critics.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The&nbsp;official selection of your work is the agency endeavor.</p>', '<h2>Agency Directors</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Since 2016, we have handle&nbsp;more than 700&nbsp;films (feature, music videos, documentaries and short movies). We set up teams to shape your film identity, push your idea and manage the workflow for success of film.</p>', '350 Selections &  AWARDS IN 2018-2019.', 'These awards are both national and international in 2018-2019', '250 Selections & AWARDS IN 2020-2022.', 'These awards are both national and international in 2020-2022', 'JYOTI SINGH', 'Director', 'SHIKHA TOMER', 'Creative Director', '1645850748-_98548702_gettyimages-104559594.jpg', '1645850748-_114319022_tv062954361.jpg');

